reviewText: I am a fine of def poetty jam to begin with...  I just had to add it to my collection.

I love Def Poetry.  I watch this DVD every chance I get.  There are some singer/poets as well as some very profound and entertaining spoken word artist.  I want to be just like them when I grow up.

Susie McCray
"See What I See"

Def Poetry allows all sorts viewpoints to be heard in a controlled atmosphere with artistic influence.  Most of the artists included are indeed bright minds that are a thrill to watch.  I think that I will purchase future seasons.  In fact, I think that it is Season 5 that I enjoyed the most on HBO. LOP O VOP E!!
